></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'></td><td style='white-space:nowrap;text-align:left;'>RTB LEG KAPA TO KRAP AT CRUISE. AOA DEICE CAWS INDICATION. RAN QRH WITH NO EFFECT. APPROX 15 MINUTES LATER IT BEGAN WORKING AGAIN. APPROX 20 MINUTES AFTER THAT, SAME THING HAPPENED. BEGAN WORKING AGAIN PRIOR TO LANDING IN RAPID CITY.</td></tr>
